{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"小红帽脱险记１０","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":11}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记１０"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我还做过一个梦："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我造了一座大花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比我们中国还要大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比我们地球还要宽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头会开花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥巴会唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚂蚁会造房子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青蛙会打大锣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老年人头发不会白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牙齿不会落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩子骑火车赛跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐飞机过河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做工比吃糖还有味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种地比过年还快活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人不欺负人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人不剥削人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家见面笑嘻嘻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有了枪炮的吓人声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没有混蛋到处拉壮丁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我的梦还没有完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖就要来吃我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃掉了我不要紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃掉了我的梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那实在太伤心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那实在太伤心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我还这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有高得象一棵树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有壮得象一条牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好坐在这里哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我的眼泪往下巴上流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈呀！………”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那老混蛋，老流氓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他睡醒了么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要来把你吃掉吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要紧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要紧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的志气高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的梦做得好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是从来不流泪，不害怕的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不要以为你太小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一棵树那么高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要以为我太小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一条牛那么壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一加一等于二，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有力量，有力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十乘十等于百，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就更有力量，更有力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——团结就是力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未必你没有听见学生们这样唱？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我早打铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚打铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打把镰力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割麦子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打把斧头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍柴烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打把犁头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕地球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打把锤子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辟山头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打把铲子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开大路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一加一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等于二，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十乘十，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等于百，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我拉风箱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你加煤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我掌钳子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你打锤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打把刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀掉老山妖。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打把刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀掉老山妖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“谢谢你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不哭了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢谢你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我快活了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但你不要又象黄狗、白马、和蜜蜂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说到说得蛮好听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃到了好的东西就又变了心。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你真是小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你真是小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么这样分不清？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不是老山妖喂养的小畜牲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖还是我的大仇人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他咬断了我爸爸的一条腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢走了我家耕田的牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还抢走我家喂来过年的大花猪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺便咬掉了我妈妈的一只手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要杀掉他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能除掉这个害！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要杀掉他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能报掉这个仇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快点来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天要黑了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们得趁早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁早打好刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀掉老山妖！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风箱扇起了血红的火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锈铁化成了血红的块块。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啦呼啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮当叮当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风箱拼命的扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤拼命的敲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啦呼啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮当叮当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风箱拚命的扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤拚命的敲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把又快又亮的刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打好了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把又快又亮的刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打好了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跛着脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弓着背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流着眼泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一拐的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走上山坡来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿着香火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿着鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口里还大声的叫："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这小鬼头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的朋友都不要你了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这回你再也逃不掉！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他把鲜花抛到了茅屋边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜蜂马上飞到了那上面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屁股一颠一颠的吸得很起劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象世界上没有什么朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没有什么敌人。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}